00:02:12.430 --> 00:02:13.680
The User's Guide."

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:20.954
And the reason why I
got to write this book

00:02:20.954 --> 00:02:26.990
is many people agree that
economics is very important.

00:02:26.990 --> 00:02:31.190
Economic events like 2008
financial crisis, or the rise

00:02:31.190 --> 00:02:35.600
