lives for better or worse.

00:02:40.681 --> 00:02:45.350
And how our business
and political leaders

00:02:45.350 --> 00:02:47.520
deal with those
changes also affect

00:02:47.520 --> 00:02:51.560
how people live, how they
grow old, how they retire,

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:54.700
and so on.

00:02:54.700 --> 00:02:59.310
So everyone agrees that economic
issues are very important.

00:02:59.310 --> 00:03:03.680
