01:00:48.490 --> 01:00:51.530
see it as a way to get rid
of the Conservative Party

01:00:51.530 --> 01:00:55.040
rather than truly be
a separate country.

01:00:55.040 --> 01:00:57.130
So yeah, they might
be in for a shock.

