Denmark has 5 million people.

01:01:12.290 --> 01:01:14.170
Austria has 7 million.

01:01:14.170 --> 01:01:15.500
Switzerland has 7 million.

01:01:15.500 --> 01:01:16.330
So why not?

01:01:16.330 --> 01:01:21.990
But this will create quite a
disruption in the short run.

01:01:21.990 --> 01:01:25.230
And yes, the UK
economy might suffer

01:01:25.230 --> 01:01:29.850
because of all this
short-term turmoil.

01:01:29.850 --> 01:01:34.990
And can it survive that
given its weakened state?

01:01:34.990 --> 01:01:35.860
I don't know.

